    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1943-08-03T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1943-08-03T00:00:00-05:00" n="260"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d260">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">Roosevelt Papers: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Assistant to the President’s Military Aide</hi> (<persName
                        type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Hammond</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the President’s Naval Aide</hi> (<persName
                        type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Brown</hi>
                    </persName>)<note n="1" xml:id="d260fn1">Brown was with Roosevelt at Birch
                        Island.</note>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">[<placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>,] <date calendar="gregorian" when="1943-08-03">3 August
                            1943</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <gloss target="#t_White1">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">White</hi>
                    </gloss> 30. In our telephone conversation at 11:10 a.m. August 3 we decided if
                    you did not call me back in 15 minutes I could assume the President had approved
                    the conditions to make Rome an open city as set out in <gloss target="#t_White1">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">White</hi>
                    </gloss> 25.<note n="2" xml:id="d260fn2">See <hi rend="italic">ante</hi>, <ref
                            target="#pg_530">p. 530</ref>, fn. 1.</note> When you did not call by
                    11:30 a.m. in accordance with the above agreement I notified General Marshall
                    the President had approved the conditions.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
